    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Field of history concerned with topics that are distinctly localized in subject matter and source materials, generally covering specific neighborhoods, communities, counties or other specific subdivisions of larger geopolitical bodies.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
